description: Happy Food Catering is here to enrich your life with an all-new way to experience healthier homegrown cuisine. From cultivation to tasty creation, this food truck is improving your meal from the very first moment. With offerings like Seared Halibut Tacos, Smoked Duck Crostin, Happy Fries (with pork confit, jalapeños, garlic, and Tillamook cheddar) and much more, of course this service is so positively pleasing. For a dining experience unlike any other, at your next big event, the heavenly deliciousness from Happy Food Catering will surely inspire happiness in your hungry guests.
name: Happy Food Catering
